A Diepsloot taxi driver is due to appear in the Randburg Magistrate s Court on Tuesday to face a murder charge.South African Police Service spokesperson, Lieutenant Kay Makhubela said when the incident happened the the policeman who was off duty and was stationed at Norkem Park SA Police Service.Constable Matsie Jacob Manabile was stabbed in the upper body, and died on arrival at a hospital on Sunday night. It is alleged that he and the suspect had an argument the suspect then took out a knife and stabbed the deceased who died in hospital, Police said.-TNA Reporter 